vation Fee  Health Insurance is required fee for all International cadets  Please contact the Office of International Programs for specific coverage information Finance Administration Home Comptroller s Home Colleague Dept Manual Forms Directory Financial Statements Newsletter Our Offices Accounts Payable Cash Receipts Fixed Assets General Ledger   Reporting Payroll Student Accounting The Cost of Attendance 2015 16 Payment Schedule Refund Policy Billing Information Payment Plans Restrictive Holds Contact Information Post View Net Price Calculator Travel Staff Lt  Col  Kevin A  Ryan Comptroller Ph   540  464 7270 Fax   540  464 7794 Smith Hall  3rd Floor Virginia Military Institute Lexington  Virginia 24450 Contact Comptrollers Office  Finance Administration Home Comptroller s Home Colleague Dept Manual Forms Directory Financial Statements Newsletter Our Offices Accounts Payable Cash Receipts Fixed Assets General Ledger   Reporting Payroll Student Accounting The Cost of Attendance 2015 16 Payment Schedule Refund Policy Billing Information Payment Plans Restrictive Holds Contact Information Post View Net Price Calculator Travel Staff Lt  Col  Kevin A  Ryan Comptroller Ph   540  464 7270 Fax   540  464 7794 Smith Hall  3rd Floor Virginia Military Institute Lexington  Virginia 24450 Contact Comptrollers Office Finance Administration Home Comptroller s Home Colleague Dept Manual Forms Directory Financial Statements Newsletter Our Offices Accounts Payable Cash Receipts Fixed Assets General Ledger   Reporting Payroll Student Accounting The Cost of Attendance 2015 16 Payment Schedule Refund Policy Billing Information Payment Plans Restrictive Holds Contact Information Post View Net Price Calculator Travel Staff Finance Administration Home Finance Administration Home Comptroller s Home Comptroller s Home Colleague Dept Manual Colleague Dept Manual Forms Directory Forms Directory Financial Statements Financial Statements Newsletter Newsletter Our Offices Accounts Payable Cash